type: software
title: "Toward FM for NPP — SmolLM2"
version: 1.0.0
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/sixticket/Toward_FM_for_NPP_SmolLM2"
abstract: "Official code for a compact 360M-parameter language model (SmolLM2) that generates physically valid PWR control-rod commands, validated through closed-loop execution in the KOMODO reactor simulator."
keywords:
  - nuclear reactor control
  - large language models
  - agentic AI
  - physical AI
  - domain-specific foundation models
  - KOMODO
  - SmolLM2
